    "Description": "You been doing good work for us, so I got a favor to ask. I'll still pay you, but it's a favor. Got some cargo that needs to get bounced from <EM4>~mission(Location|Address)</EM4> to <EM4>~mission(Destination|Address)</EM4> and the guy that was supposed to do it found himself on the wrong side of an airlock, but hey, shit still needs to get done.\n\nOnly thing is you'll need a ship that can carry <EM4>~mission(MissionMaxSCUSize) cargo containers</EM4>.  A <EM4>handheld tractor beam</EM4> would also be smart to bring along. \n\nIf you could sort it out for me, that'd be great.\n\n- Stows out",
